Usage:
    mediasplit.pl [-a action] [-c] [-d dest] [-e] [-h] [-m media] [-p style] [-s] source_dir
    
        -a action    (print | copy | move | none)
        -c           calculate minimum disc size
        -d dest      destination directory for copy or move
        -e           split based on episode names in filename into Series/ep.avi
        -f           split maintaining directory affinity
        -g           split episodic materiel for burning
        -h           help (this screen)
        -m media     (dvd | cd)
        -n number    start with media number
        -p style     (tree | flat) prints directory tree
        -s           split based on size
        -v           generate SFV files (requires CFV)
